</p>

</div>

<div class="card">

<h3>CIT Certified Prompt Engineer</h3>

<p>
Certified in Prompt Engineering with knowledge of AI tools,
productivity, and modern digital technologies.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="skills">

<h2 class="title">My Skills</h2>

<div class="skills">

<div class="skill">
<h4>WordPress Development</h4>
<div class="bar">
<div class="fill" style="width:95%;"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="skill">
<h4>Frontend Development</h4>
<div class="bar">
<div class="fill" style="width:90%;"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="skill">
<h4>HTML & CSS</h4>
<div class="bar">
<div class="fill" style="width:95%;"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="skill">
<h4>JavaScript</h4>
<div class="bar">
<div class="fill" style="width:80%;"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="skill">
<h4>Teaching</h4>
<div class="bar">
<div class="fill" style="width:85%;"></div>
</div>
</div>

<div class="skill">
<h4>Prompt Engineering</h4>
<div class="bar">
<div class="fill" style="width:90%;"></div>
</div>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact">

<h2 class="title">Contact Me</h2>

<div class="contact">

<form>

<input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>

<input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>

<textarea placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>

<button type="submit">Send Message</button>

</form>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

<p>© 2026 Dua | WordPress Developer & Frontend Developer | All Rights Reserved</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
